title: Diary of a Hitman w/ Sammy The Bull
itunes:title: Diary of a Hitman w/ Sammy The Bull
description:
We have a sit down with former Gambino Family underboss/hitman Sammy The Bull and we discuss the business of contract killings, the current state of the government, his thoughts on Candace Owens and much more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
